    <abstract>Fa Weitang gives two entries for „Xiao Tieshan” and corrected the mistakes which Sun
        Xingyan 孫星衍 made in his 《寰宇訪碑録》. It is unclear how he was able to make the corrections. The
        titles of Fa Weitang’s entries read: “匡喆刻經頌“ Hymn to the engraved sūtra by Kuang Zhe
        ‘小鐵山摩崖殘字八種’ Eight kinds of damaged characters of the rock cut inscription. There is one more
        entry which is not being related to Tieshan, but which was also taken from Sun Xingyan:
        “趙郡李巨教磨崖題字” Rock cut colophon by Li Jujiao of Zhao Commandery</abstract>
